name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: SaveItems for dropshipping in Google Sheets

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Saveitems - Save items for dropshipping in Google Sheets

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
On the sales page, and on the supplier page, you can save the product and insert the Google Spreadsheet

From the extension, we save the product on the sales page and save the product on the supplier page. The site displays all saved products.

New features will be added in the extension and there will be new features on the site.

The site has items that you can save that are sold on the Ebay site.

Expanding works on sites Amazon.com / Ebay.com / Walmart.com - More sites will be added later
